  "response": "Airplanes are not designed to float on water like boats are. Most commercial airplanes will sink if they land on water, although some have the ability to float for a short period of time, allowing for emergency evacuations. There are, however, specific types of aircraft called floatplanes or seaplanes that are designed to take off from and land on water, and these do float.",
